The popular Nigerian comedian, entertainer, skit making, and social media influencer, Samuel Animashaun Perry, professionally known as Broda Shaggi has caused reactions on social media after sharing a good news on his official Instagram page. He revealed that he just signed a muilt-million Naira endorsement with a big company in Nigeria.
Broda Shaggi is one of the followed skits maker in Nigeria. She has almost ten million followers on Instagram, and many of his followers have congratulated him.
While sharing the pictures, he wrote:
“I am Proud to announce my partnership with a company (name withheld)
Let’s make your dreams a reality.
A lot of surprises coming your way”
Read how top Nigerian celebrities and his Instagram followers congratulated him in the comments section on Instagram



